.DT
check_book_same
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
check_book_same

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
check_book_same -  Checks to see if the passed in book is the same as the current book number that is set on it.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
int check_book_same(object book,
int num)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^book%^RESET%^ - the book to check
%^BOLD%^num%^RESET%^ - the book number to check against
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/book_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

Checks to see if the passed in book is the same as the current book
number that is set on it.  We only look at the text and ignore the
type and language with which it is written.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
compare_pages(), add_book()

.EP

